              SEGMITE publishes an Open-access, Quarterly International Journal of Economic and
              Environmental Geology (IJEEG) with ISSN: 2223-957 X. It is a peer-reviewed
              multidisciplinary, open archive international journal published since 2010 in Karachi,
              Pakistan. This online international journal is dedicated to publish original research
              work related to the fields of Economic and Environmental Geology. IJEEG is indexed by
              various databases including the Directory of Open Access Journals (DOAJ), Academia,
              ISI, ASI, SEMANTIC SCHOLAR, Cross Ref. (DOI), Euro Pub, Google, BASE and Science Open
              etc.
